This paper discusses a meta-querying system for databases, which is a topic closely related to database management (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of XML and XSLT, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL) applications. Additionally, the paper discusses the extension of SQL, which is a fundamental language in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
